Name: Gatekeeper: Eclipse
About the game: In Gatekeeper: Eclipse you'll find: Three unique locations of The Nowhere. Around 1000 enemies will rush you in order to steal the Heart of Time. Various Gates to defend from the waves of enemies. New mechanic: the enemies will emerge from the portals. If you don't clear the location from all enemies, they will follow you to the next lvl. Free skills on each lvl. The prologue includes two endings.
